  lset applyto = (3) nucmodel=4by4 nst=2 rates=invgamma covarion=no; [K80+I+G]

        unlink statefreq=(all) revmat=(all) shape=(all) pinvar=(all);
        prset applyto=(all) ratepr=variable;

       
        outgroup Didelphis_virginiana;

	outgroup Didelphis_virginiana;
	constraint root=1-.;
	constraint marsupalia = 1-3;
	constraint boreotheria = 6-19 ;
	constraint Atlantogenata = 20-132;
	constraint Xenarthra = 20-22;
	constraint crownPlacentalia = 6-132;
	constraint Afrotheria = 23-132;
	constraint Paeungulata= 83-132;
	constraint Proboscidea = 108-125;
	constraint Sirenia = 126-132;
	constraint Hyracoidea = 83-107;
	constraint Macroscelidea = 62-78;
	constraint crownMacroscelidea = 62-77;
	constraint Chrysochchloridae = 42-61;
	constraint hyrax = Dendrohyrax_dorsalis Heterohyrax_brucei Procavia_capensis Thyrohyrax_domorictus Thyrohyrax_litholagus Thyrohyrax_meyeri Thyrohyrax_pygmaeus Titanohyrax_andrewsi 	Titanohyrax_angustidens Titanohyrax_sp__nov Saghatherium_antiquum Saghatherium_bowni Selenohyrax_chatrathi Pachyhyrax_crassidentatus Megalohyrax_eocaenus Megalohyrax_sp__nov 	Geniohyus_diphycus Geniohyus_mirus Bunohyrax_fajumensis Bunohyrax_major Afrohyrax_championi Antilohyrax_pectidens;
	constraint afroinsectophilia = 23-82;
	constraint rhync =  Rhynchocyon_chrysopygus Rhynchocyon_cirnei Rhynchocyon_petersi Rhynchocyon_udzungwensis;



	calibrate  Afrohyrax_championi = uniform(11.6, 20.4)	
		   Antilohyrax_pectidens = uniform(28.4, 33.9)
	           Arcanotherium_savagei = uniform(32.8, 37.2)

                   Thyrohyrax_pygmaeus = uniform(28.4, 33.9)

	           Titanohyrax_sp__nov = uniform(28.4, 33.9)
	           Widanelfarasia_bowni = uniform(28.4, 33.9)
	          ;
	prset brlenspr=clock:fossilization; 
	prset clockvarpr= igr;	
	prset  igrvarpr=exp(30.57326);  
	prset nodeagepr=calibrated;
	prset clockratepr = lognorm(-5.383875, 2.458582);
	prset topologypr=constraints(root, marsupalia, boreotheria, hyrax, rhync, Atlantogenata, Xenarthra, crownPlacentalia, Afrotheria, Paeungulata, Proboscidea, 	Sirenia, Hyracoidea, Macroscelidea, crownMacroscelidea);
	prset SampleStrat=FossilTip;

	calibrate marsupalia = offsetexp(47.8, 70.29);
	calibrate crownPlacentalia = offsetexp(61.6, 89.53);
	calibrate boreotheria = offsetexp(61.5, 89.52);
